{"tid":1734743,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［唔好拉］發現左一個好危險既敵人","createTime":"2019-11-18T11:47:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T12:18:56.000Z","uid":311120,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"73500991bdc49f0149e793c6bc4d3c4c405e2738","tid":1734743,"uid":311120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T11:47:56.000Z","msg":"見到琴晚埋土既情況<br />\n就留意到<br />\n接落黎既敵人係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">冬天</span></span>啊<br />\n唔好睇少冬天 唔做好準備一定比狗壓<br />\n<br />\n1.寒冷天氣<br />\n<br />\n雖然香港唔會跌到零下幾度 但相對冷空氣會下沉<br />\n雲層會下降 污染物都一樣<br />\n特別係二噁英山埃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到時候無論守城定煲底 豬嘴會變為必需品<br />\n勸大家做好準備 除左禦寒衣物<br />\n仲要留意空氣污染 <br />\n根據自己能力決定出唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.水炮車<br />\n埋土既手足琴晚已經經歷過<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n比水射中真係會凍到仆街<br />\n到時重要著好多件衫<br />\n唔單止負荷多左<br />\n體溫都會快速下降<br />\n守城既手足 係呢d情況會好難挨<br />\n嚴重可能失溫<br />\n唔好痴線用汽油彈取暖<br />\nD氣體點都會有害 特別對呼吸系統<br />\n暫時未諗到方法對抗<br />\n一起集思廣益啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3.病<br />\n唔好睇少呢樣嘢<br />\n你病左真係唔好周圍走<br />\n你身體弱 好容易無力同暈<br />\n比狗追捉到拖累到前線就唔好啦<br />\n同埋on9 d咁講<br />\n傳染到比人就唔好啦<br />\n各位睇住啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n真心睇到琴晚埋土 真係好擔心之後既日子點算<br />\n希望大家有咩對策就提出 打好個底<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"0c1984b65140993a3335a6b750c0c77bbd7ec57a","tid":1734743,"uid":337761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T11:48:13.000Z","msg":"Twitter組24時keep住更新<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">幫手retweet+ like + reply</span> <br />\n㩒入----&gt; <a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=O2Kpqs6hAe%2BpM%2F1AUa5ix85Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=e381b5bc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打 <span style=\"color: gold;\"> /task3</span> <br />\n<br />\n最新Task分類<br />\n/task1: 法案、抗爭活動<br />\n/task2: BNO、中國、其他香港議題<br />\n/task3: !!!! #PolyU !!!!<br />\n/task4: 日韓德任務"},{"pid":"ea50dd5cc0f5f22e177787bdedda90d4221bb10f","tid":1734743,"uid":311120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T11:50:51.000Z","msg":"推啊 雖然好common sense 但都想大家睇到"},{"pid":"2eec9050aa55f6749dba239a2b3b4eeef12e349c","tid":1734743,"uid":311120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T11:53:44.000Z","msg":"自推一"},{"pid":"4dae71fa1d497640a46afc623ba473b3bff8b474","tid":1734743,"uid":311120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T11:53:54.000Z","msg":"自推二"},{"pid":"cd885d94fcc9167098aa688803da2e797b93f66f","tid":1734743,"uid":311120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T11:54:04.000Z","msg":"自推三"},{"pid":"6a337aba4bae7abce6080b3c7ca541b6db5bf84d","tid":1734743,"uid":311120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T11:54:15.000Z","msg":"自推四"},{"pid":"c6460ad5200ed4a2936aad809d60d426b799feb0","tid":1734743,"uid":311120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T11:54:26.000Z","msg":"自推五"},{"pid":"c3621e214fbec723f6669aa087d01732ebd7ca4a","tid":1734743,"uid":311120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T11:54:37.000Z","msg":"自推六"},{"pid":"6a2b0e3adc00beaf2aa74b1bc5cda37fc08d1689","tid":1734743,"uid":311120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T11:54:48.000Z","msg":"自推七"},{"pid":"a5e0f07c4c205e4ef47302a13ceb59e0e1d2f851","tid":1734743,"uid":311120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T11:54:58.000Z","msg":"自推八"},